summary: I am an international business professional with 10+ years of experience in a wide variety of industries. During the past decade I’ve been part of, or worked side by side with many world-renowned companies, including my current team at Bolt, Uber, Google, Seedstars, Telia Sonera, and many early stage startups. Those companies are changing the world for better, and I am lucky enough to be there to contribute my part.
